MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 953295728}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 04673aa0fd54847459f738969017ecfd, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Dialogue4
  ScavengerLines:
  - INCREDIBLE!
  - YOU DID IT!
  - I sure was wrong about you...
  - 'Well, a promise is a promise... '
  - If you follow the path north west of the shuttle, you will find a building that
    leads to an undergound chamber. Rumour has it that the humans used it for shelter
    before.. welll.. you know...
  - I've unlocked the entrance using my cortical processor, all you need to do is
    go and press the power button to disable the security gate.
  - You shouldn't run into too much trouble down there... although, the place is
    ancient. You may encounter breakages in power lines that you need to bypass somehow...
  - Afterwards be sure to recharge and head to the gate north of the shuttle. From
    there you will be able to escape the scrapyard.
  - Yeah... well anyways. Goodluck, and goodbye!
  DialogueIndex: 0
  DialogueUi4: {fileID: 625796712}
  UIlinker4: {fileID: 953295728}
  Player: {fileID: 304904380}
  InteractProximity: 20
  dialogueui: {fileID: 625796715}
  ScavengerArmOnPlayer: {fileID: 1102415988}
  scavengerArmOnScav: {fileID: 1056244247}
  PlayerMove: {fileID: 3828621389755395}
  PlayerShoot: {fileID: 3828621389755394}
